  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Village Montana Apartments are offered on a self-catering board basis.</p>
<p>The residence has a bakery delivery service available to book locally, and if you want to take the stress out of meal times, there’s the possibility to upgrade to 'Half Board'. This will include breakfast and evening meals (drinks are not included).</p>
<p>Breakfast will be a continental buffet breakfast with some additional hot options, usually served from 07:30 – 10am. This is taken in the Restaurant ‘Les Chanterelles’ which is located in the main hotel building of this complex.</p>
<p>Enjoy a five course à la carte evening meal with choice of menu and waiter service at 'Les Chanterelles', a traditional French restaurant. Or book into their other two restaurants - choose between 'La Chaumiere' (Savoyarde specialities) or a traditional brasserie 'La Place' in Chalet Montana Platon at the entrance to the complex.</p>
<p>The restaurants can also be booked and paid for locally if you stick to the standard self-catering board basis. Opening times may vary, but are usually from 7 – 9:30pm. Please note that some dishes may have an additional supplement.</p>
<p>Christmas Dinner and New Years Galas are available to pre book, and there are additional supplements for these gala dinners.</p>
<p>Earlier meal times for children are available (on request, during French school holidays).</p>
<p>Alternatively, we've partnered up with <strong>Huski</strong> who provide premium oven ready meals across the French Alps. Huski will deliver your meals directly to your accommodation in time for your arrival, all you'll have to do is cook. If you'd like to know more, please click <a rel="noopener" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/special-offers/huski-food-drink-delivery-service" target="_blank">here</a> for further details.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
