  <description><![CDATA[<p>This unique resort complex offers a variety of residences in a serene, slope-side setting. These apartments are comfortable, spacious, and in a range of sizes, which makes them ideal for families and groups.</p>
<h2>Slope side location</h2>
<p>The Village Montana apartments are a wonderful place to experience the charm of the Alps while enjoying all the modern comforts. You'll feel right at home in their convenient and quiet location in <a data-udi="umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565" href="/{localLink:umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565}" title="Tignes">Tignes</a>. The residence is made up of five apartment buildings which are close to the slopes, with some even benefitting from being on the edge of the piste. You can simply make your way onto the fantastic <a data-udi="umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03}" title="Tignes-Val d’Isere Ski Area">Tignes-Val d'Isere Ski Area</a>, and with private ski lockers returning back to the residence at the end of the day couldn't be easier.</p>
<h2>Soothing spa and relaxation</h2>
<p>After a day of exploring the <a data-udi="umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03}" title="Tignes-Val d’Isere Ski Area">Tignes- Val d'Isere Ski Are</a>a, there is nowhere nicer to be than in the hotels wellness area. For a little extra, you can pay to use the lovely wellness area '<span>Les Bains du Montana'</span>, featuring a heated outdoor pool, and a spa area with a sauna, hammam and hot tubs to sooth your achy ski legs. </p>
<h2>Well equipped</h2>
<p>Each of the apartments has a well equipped kitchenette so you can whip up tasty meals, the supermarket is only a short walk away so you can stock up on the necessities. To take the hassle out of choosing what's for dinner, why not consider booking a <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/special-offers/huski-food-drink-delivery-service">Huski</a> package - Huski deliver high quality oven meals to you, you just need to pop it in the oven and enjoy.</p>
<p>If you don't feel like cooking, reserve a table and treat your taste buds in one of the lovely Village Montana restaurants, serving Savoyard dishes influenced by the fresh and regional produce. </p>]]></description>
