  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Two bedroom apartments</strong> sleep two to four people and are approximately 45m². Each apartment has two twin bedrooms, a living room, a kitchenette, and a bathroom. </p>
<p><strong>Two bedroom apartments with a sofa bed</strong> sleep three to six people and are approximately 55m². Each apartment has one twin and one double bedroom,  a living room with a double sofa bed, a kitchenette, and a bathroom with a bath or shower.  This apartment type may be a duplex.</p>
<p><strong>Three bedroom apartments</strong> sleep three to six people and are approximately 55m². Each apartment has three twin bedrooms, a living area, a kitchenette, and a bathroom with a bath or shower. This apartment type may be a duplex.</p>
<p><strong>Three bedroom apartments with fireplace </strong>sleep three to six people and are approximately 65m². Each apartment has three twin bedrooms, a living area with a fireplace and a balcony, a kitchenette and two bathrooms with a bath or shower.</p>
<p><strong>Five bedroom apartments</strong> sleep eight to ten people and are around 100m². The apartment is made up as a two bedroom and three bedroom apartment with a communal front door. Some apartments have a fireplace. </p>
<p><strong>Apartment facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Most apartments have a private balcony with mountain views</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Satellite TV</li>
<li>Fully equipped kitchenette with oven, microwave, kettle and toaster, coffee maker, hotplates, fridge and dishwasher</li>
<li>Living room</li>
<li>Bath with shower head attachment or shower room</li>
<li>WC</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Cleaning kit</li>
<li>Bed linen and towels (mid week towel change available)</li>
<li>Beds are made on arrival</li>
<li>End of stay cleaning, except the kitchen</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Airelles Building</strong></p>
<p><strong>Three bedroom duplex apartments</strong> sleeps six to eight people and are around 100m², split across two levels. The lower level has a living area and a twin room with an en-suite shower, cabin room and a shower room with a WC. The upper level has two twin bedrooms, a bathroom with a hydro massage bath and WC and a sauna. There is also a fireplace in the lounge.</p>
<p><img src="/media/13090601/village-montana-5-bedroom-apartment-floorplan.png?width=0&amp;height=0" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/a045189781e241889a3607a81db402ee" /><img style="width: 0px; height: 0px;" src="/media/13090601/village-montana-5-bedroom-apartment-floorplan.png?width=0&amp;height=0" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/a045189781e241889a3607a81db402ee" /></p>
<p><strong>Airelles apartment facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Living room with a fireplace</li>
<li>Satellite TV</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Balcony with views across the resort and surrounding mountains</li>
<li>Sauna</li>
<li>Cleaning kit</li>
<li>Bed linen</li>
<li>Towels (mid week towel change available)</li>
<li>Beds are made on arrival</li>
<li>End of stay cleaning, except the kitchen</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
